Title: 150+ Austrian Crystal 3D Bow French Clip Hair Jewelry Barrette in Ombre Shades
Description: ~~~Welcome to My Store! ~~~ Be sure to check out my ME page for my blog and my stores Item Description This listing is for one gorgeous three dimensional bow shaped hair barrette made from an antiqued silver tine color metal. It is self adjusting and a French clip barrette style- not made in France- the mechanism style is called a french clip. It is adorned with over 150 sparkling AB Sapphire blue color, Sapphire color, and Purple color genuine Austrian Crystals. It measures 2 3/4 inches long by 1 3/8 inches (at the widest part). It sits 3/8 of an inch high and the barrette mechanism on the back is 2 3/8 inches long. The barrette is self adjusting to hold both fine and coarse thick hair. It has a very slight graceful head hugging curve to it. This is a Medium Large barrette- please use a ruler to approximate the measurements at home. The crystals are purple on the outer side edges changing to AB blue to blue in the center. The crystals are also on the "inside" of the Bow.Absolutely stunning!See additional photos at the top left of this ad. Brand new and in perfect condition and sent boxed for protection in shipping!
